        "action": "A2 motorcycle licences to upgrade to an A license automatically after 2 years",
        "additional_details": "This is instead of taking the same practical examination two times.\r\n\r\nIn the past, an A2 rider would wait for two years before automatically achieving a full unrestricted motorcycle license. I propose we now return to that scheme again.",
        "background": "To revert to the automatic update of an A2 license to a full A license after 2 years of riding.",
